        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn Faddal has been transmitted by me from my father - may Allah (swt) be pleased with him - from Sad ibn Abdullah, from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa, from Al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn Faddal."
